sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant Guard as JWT Auth Guard
    participant Tenant as TenantContext Interceptor
    participant Ctrl as Any Controller
    participant DB as Database (Prisma)

    C->>Guard: GET /bookings (Bearer token)
    Guard->>Guard: decode and verify JWT
    Guard->>DB: load user by sub
    Guard->>DB: check user.isActive
    Guard->>DB: check tenant.isActive (if user has tenantId)
    Guard->>Guard: attach CurrentUserPayload to request

    Guard->>Tenant: request with user context
    Tenant->>Tenant: extract user.tenantId
    Tenant->>Tenant: set request.tenantId

    Tenant->>Ctrl: request with tenant context
    Ctrl->>DB: query with tenantId filter
    Ctrl-->>Tenant: response
    Tenant->>Tenant: ResponseTransformInterceptor
    Tenant-->>C: {success: true, data: {...}}
